data.description: Amazing One story with great location!  * New Roof * Updated Double Pane Windows * Huge lot with newer fence and double wide gate *  Come see this charming home with 3 generously sized bedrooms and large closets.  Cozy family room with glowing fireplace is open to both kitchen and breakfast area and has updated flooring.  Step outside to find one of the largest lots in the neighborhood.  10 minutes or less to the Hardy Toll Rd., I45, & 99 Grand Parkway.  Convenient location for commute or shopping!
